Text: Commencing memory fabrication... Thou standest before Tiamat, guardian of Meracydia.
Go forth, my children! Drive these foul invaders from our home!
My boundless rage shall swallow thee whole!
The flames of retribution consume thee!
Bear witness to the power of the first brood!
Intruders detected. Initializing defensive protocols.
Consciousness injection successful. Commencing attack protocol.
Sustained enemy presence detected. Threat level increased and attack pattern elevated in intensity.
Welcome one, welcome all, to Kageyama's Clockwork Castletown! Gahahaha!
Fires and fights are the flowers of Kugane! Now, entertain me, peasants!
Hm, needs more sound and fury... Let the parade commence!
Dance, my puppets, dance! But have care where you wander...
Now, you can't expect clockwork to do all the work for you.
Oh, I seem to have dropped a coin. And another. And another!
Eat, fight... Eat, fight...
Death brings me no peace... Such is my fate...
Few can wield such power as mine!
Entertain me, my darlings!
My every breath is laced with magicks!
Another...fleeting diversion...
Always more killin' to be done... And I'm always happy to oblige!
Make it fun for me, eh?
The first drops are always the sweetest!
Ungh... Guess my time's up...
GRAAAHHH!
GRRRHH!
Disturbed once again...?
Crumble and die!
My strength is without equal!
This shouldn't kill you...
It ain't a fight till the dying begins!
I've had enough of you!
I'll leave you bloody and battered!
You will suffer!
For Lady Athena!
The end...comes!
It isn't over!
Defeat Kokytos
Flames take you!
Ice bind you!
Clear Mount Rokkon
Clear the Single Step
Defeat Shishio
Clear the Clever Roost
Defeat Gorai the Uncaged
Defeat Moko the Restless
Three paths to be unsealed at our behest. Whither shall we wander?
You thought to go down this path as well? How reassuring!
Interested in a different path? I shall place my trust in your intuition.
A grand gate. What lies beyond, I wonder?
I espy a most promising pagoda! Let us make it our destination.
What curious creatures! They must have been emboldened by these terrible torrents.
Mountain weather is wont to change on a whim, but 'tis not nature's whims at work here...
Thank the kami the rains have ceased... We should make for shelter ere another storm passes through.
Such tumultuous spirits! Servants of the wind, no doubt.
These winds could blow a man away...and will, if we do not tread carefully!
A thousand thousand paths...and yours ends here.
Fill your lungs!
Dying embers are easily snuffed...
We are everything and nothing─your first and final breath!
Choke in your graves!
Slayer of spirits... Their fate will soon be yours!
Your soul is mine to claim! Your marrow, mine to burn...
These treasures are mine! All mine! You shall not sully their brilliance!
The head monk, I take it? And bearing a form befitting his proclivities...

火の神より賜りし力よ……
琵琶の響きで、燃え立ち猛れ！

火の神より賜りし力よ……
琵琶の音色で、分かれて増えよ！
Beware the biwa's melody, <split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>! It resounds with power...

専門外なので私にはさっぱりデスが、
アナタなら、演奏の違いもわかるのでは……？
A song to guide you to your grave!

Beads to bind the spirit's form...
With these words, be reborn!
My blessings are your curse!
No mercy, no mercy!
Hee hee! You thought you were free of me!
Divine thunder, heed my call─bestow upon my biwa your tumultuous timbre!
My power will see you humbled!
A drink to fuel the fires of my fury!
Ahahaha! You are as nothing before my might!
Curses... The libations...!
You yet stand!?
No... My precious...treasures...
Divine fire, I beseech thee─cleanse the branded with blessed flame!
Divine thunder, heed my call─sound to rend the very earth!
There is no salvation for thieves... I offer you death, and nothing more!
It shall be mine...mine, I say! You cannot have it!
The dance of a thousand petals begins with a single blossom!
Wayward flowers, bend to my will!
Spring has come!
Embrace ephemerality!
My shadow is my strength!
In summer's blaze do my blades sing... In winter's chill do they bite!
The sky weeps, and the earth heeds her call!
